          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1649848099207-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>basa</strong> with the <strong>ginger pak choi</strong> and <strong>edamame</strong> <strong>rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out</p><p>Spoon the<strong> teriyaki sauce</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
